knowledge_graph.title: Marketing de afiliación (Affiliate marketing)
knowledge_graph.description: Marketing de afiliación es una rama del marketing online que se basa en la consecución de resultados. Las empresas o sitios web, llamados afiliados, se encargan de publicitar a los comerciantes mediante la publicación de sus anuncios o promociones.

related_questions.question: What is an affiliate program and how does it work?
related_questions.snippet: Simply put, affiliate programs, also called associate programs, are arrangements in which an online merchant Web site pays affiliate Web sites a commission to send them traffic. These affiliate Web sites post links to the merchant site and are paid according to a particular agreement.
related_questions.title: What Are Affiliate Programs? - How Affiliate Programs Work ...

related_questions.question: What is being an affiliate?
related_questions.snippet: Definition: A way for a company to sell its products by signing up individuals or companies ("affiliates") who market the company's products for a commission. There are two ways to approach affiliate marketing: You can offer an affiliate program to others or you can sign up to be another business's affiliate.
related_questions.title: Affiliate Marketing Definition - Entrepreneur Small Business ...

related_questions.question: What exactly is affiliate marketing?
related_questions.snippet: Affiliate marketing is the process of earning a commission by promoting other people's (or company's) products. You find a product you like, promote it to others and earn a piece of the profit for each sale that you make.
related_questions.title: Affiliate Marketing Made Simple: A Step-by-Step Guide - Neil Patel

organic_results.title: What is Affiliate Program? - Definition from Techopedia
organic_results.snippet: An affiliate program is an automated electronic program that involves a Web advertiser and recruited webmasters. The webmasters, as affiliates, place the company's advertisements on their individually owned websites. The ads in affiliate programs are linked to company websites and are referred to as affiliate links.
